    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/8d9271962af75e7b44ed07ec56aab7e3.avif?t=1682010912\" width=352 height=82 /></span><br>The survivors is a game in an open world populated by zombies and fanatical rebels but also survivors helped, craft and base bulding, missions are to be discovered<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > What Is the Survivors</h2></h2>Your transport plane has crashed you must survive the crash in a world populated by zombies and fanatics<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Game Features</h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover A World Rich In Original Places</li></ul></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/800bb66dfef6fd845b6296be23230838.avif?t=1682010912\" width=570 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><li> Fight Different Style Of Zombies<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2></li><li> Fight Armed Fanatics<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/2b090ef6629dcbb64b987ade40f1de98.avif?t=1682010912\" width=576 height=198 /></span><br></li><li> build its base, manage its electricity, its resources, recruit npc's which will produce building materials, ammunition, care<br></li><li> stop the proliferation of zombies by making traps<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Collect figurines from this world to decorate your base<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet other factions, complete helicopter rescue missions, reconstruction missions, delivery missions, deliver civilians, buy vehicles as rewards</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/3a88ff1aa99a7f31a7493e66bcd61953.avif?t=1682010912\" width=580 height=170 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Gameplay Style </strong></h2></h2></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >it's An Survival Game Style.</h2></h2>it's a deliberately arcade style, oriented on missions and action, and the discovery of the world, here you will only have few weapons in the often identical game play, no zombies to kill at 100m.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Developpement : Road Map </strong></h2></h2>we plan to to add new vehicles and their improvements, zombie bosses, new missions and a trade system between factions....<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/908adfcea82c3cb09194997622f86f6f.avif?t=1682010912\" width=580 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >what to Enjoy</h2></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/fadc5d048c9a49d4166321795e2112eb.poster.avif?t=1682010912\" width=704 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/fadc5d048c9a49d4166321795e2112eb.webm?t=1682010912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264410/extras/fadc5d048c9a49d4166321795e2112eb.mp4?t=1682010912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul></li>",
